edu.harvard.pass.parser

Interface Parser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CPLParser, DDGParser, OPMParser, PhyloXMLParser, RDFParser, TwigParser

    public interface Parser
    A parser for provenance graphs. The parser is assumed to keep internal state, so it is usually a bad idea to reuse the same parser object for multiple unrelated files.
    Author:
    Peter Macko

    • Method Detail

      • initialize

        void initialize(java.net.URI uri)
         throws ParserException
        Initialize the parser given an input URI. If the file has an ambiguous type (such as *.xml), the method should check whether the file has a proper format that can be handled by the parser.
        Parameters:
        uri - the input URI
        Throws:
        ParserException - on error
        ParserFormatException - if the file does not have the appropriate format
